\ i-times ( xt n -- ) — run xt n times, pushing the index 0..n-1 before each call.

\ basic: print 0 1 2 3 4
[: . :] 5 i-times cr

\ zero count: never runs
[: "boom" . :] 0 i-times

\ index is the only thing pushed; quotation that ignores it leaves it
[: drop :] 3 i-times .s clear cr

\ sum of 0..9 via accumulator: 45
: sum-up-to | acc | 0 to acc  [: acc + to acc :] swap i-times  acc ;
10 sum-up-to . cr

\ sum of squares 0..4: 0+1+4+9+16 = 30
: sum-sq | acc | 0 to acc  [: dup * acc + to acc :] swap i-times  acc ;
5 sum-sq . cr

\ wrong types
[: drop :] -1 i-times
"x" [: drop :] i-times
5 5 i-times
